1
00:00:01,035 --> 00:00:04,665
Daniel: ONE DAY OF THE WEEK
I HAVE NO LECTURES,

2
00:00:04,705 --> 00:00:06,665
NO OFFICE HOURS,
NO OBLIGATIONS OF ANY KIND...

3
00:00:06,707 --> 00:00:09,337
...THE ONE DAY THAT I-I GET
A LITTLE SOLITUDE, YOU KNOW,

4
00:00:09,377 --> 00:00:11,177
A LITTLE "ME" TIME, A CHANCE
TO DO SOME ACTUAL WRITING.

5
00:00:11,212 --> 00:00:12,412
HALEY TWISTED MY ARM.

6
00:00:12,446 --> 00:00:14,276
YOUR ARM IS MINE TO TWIST,
NOT HALEY'S.

7
00:00:14,315 --> 00:00:16,015
DID HE EVEN SAY
WHAT THIS WAS ABOUT?

8
00:00:16,050 --> 00:00:17,350
[ APPLAUSE ]

9
00:00:17,385 --> 00:00:18,685
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

10
00:00:18,719 --> 00:00:21,119
DANIEL, IT IS MY HONOR
TO INFORM YOU

11
00:00:21,155 --> 00:00:23,785
THAT YOU HAVE BEEN AWARDED
THIS YEAR'S DAVENPORT PRIZE

12
00:00:23,824 --> 00:00:26,294
FOR EXPLORATION IN SCIENCE.

13
00:00:26,327 --> 00:00:28,797
I-I SWEAR,
I KNEW NOTHING ABOUT THIS.

14
00:00:28,829 --> 00:00:30,929
AND, AS I'M SURE
YOU ARE AWARE,

15
00:00:30,964 --> 00:00:33,274
THIS AWARD IS NOT JUST
ABOUT THE LAURELS

16
00:00:33,301 --> 00:00:35,441
YOU BRING TO YOURSELF
AND THE UNIVERSITY.

17
00:00:35,469 --> 00:00:40,469
IT'S ALSO ABOUT THE $50,000
CHECK THAT GOES ALONG WITH IT.

18
00:00:40,508 --> 00:00:43,438
TO DANIEL PIERCE.

19
00:00:43,477 --> 00:00:44,747
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

20
00:00:46,347 --> 00:00:47,477
[ CORK POPS ]

21
00:00:47,515 --> 00:00:49,475
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

22
00:00:49,517 --> 00:00:52,247
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

23
00:00:58,826 --> 00:01:00,456
DANIEL.

24
00:01:00,494 --> 00:01:02,504
HOW COULD YOU
BLINDSIDE ME LIKE THAT?

25
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:05,230
YOU ARE MAKING ME LOOK BAD
IN FRONT OF THE CHANCELLOR.

26
00:01:05,266 --> 00:01:09,566
THE MAN PUT YOU UP FOR THIS
PRIZE, FOR GOODNESS SAKES.

27
00:01:09,603 --> 00:01:11,913
JUST ONE HANDSHAKE.
THAT'S ALL I'M ASKING.

28
00:01:11,939 --> 00:01:13,239
KATE.

29
00:01:13,274 --> 00:01:16,114
PLEASE TELL ME
YOU'RE HERE ABOUT A CASE.

30
00:01:16,144 --> 00:01:18,854
YEPaul: MS. MORETTI,--

31
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:20,609
I AGREED TO ALLOW DANIEL
TO CONSULT WITH THE FBI

32
00:01:20,648 --> 00:01:22,618
SO LONG AS IT DIDN'T INTERFERE
WITH HIS ACADEMIC DUTIES.

33
00:01:22,650 --> 00:01:24,320
AND RIGHT NOW YOU ARE
INTERFERING WITH --

34
00:01:24,352 --> 00:01:26,152
ACTUALLY, I'M HERE
TO TALK TO YOU.

35
00:01:27,288 --> 00:01:28,688
TO ME?

36
00:01:28,722 --> 00:01:31,492
YEAH, LISTEN, A JOGGER
WAS FOUND SHOT IN THE BACK

37
00:01:31,525 --> 00:01:33,125
IN THE NATIONAL FOREST
PRESERVE.

38
00:01:33,161 --> 00:01:34,731
WE'RE HAVING TROUBLE
MAKING AN I.D.

39
00:01:34,762 --> 00:01:36,702
THERE'S NO WALLET ON HIM,
NO MATCH ON THE FINGERPRINTS.

40
00:01:36,730 --> 00:01:37,830
WHAT HAS THIS GOT TO DO
WITH HIM?

41
00:01:37,865 --> 00:01:39,325
ALL WE'VE GOT TO GO ON

42
00:01:39,367 --> 00:01:40,697
ARE SOME TATTOOS
ON THE BODY

43
00:01:40,734 --> 00:01:42,374
WHICH APPEAR TO BE
RELIGIOUS IN NATURE,

44
00:01:42,403 --> 00:01:45,213
AND DEAN HALEY'S COURSE
ON SPIRITUAL ICONOGRAPHY

45
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:47,879
WAS ONE OF THE BEST CLASSES
I EVER TOOK.

46
00:01:47,908 --> 00:01:49,608
I'M FLATTERED
YOU REMEMBER.

47
00:01:49,643 --> 00:01:51,153
ANYHOW, I'M HOPING YOU COULD
TAKE A LOOK AT THE TATTOOS,

48
00:01:51,179 --> 00:01:53,509
LET ME KNOW IF THERE'S
ANYTHING ABOUT THEM

49
00:01:53,547 --> 00:01:55,117
THAT COULD HELP ME
I.D. THE VICTIM.

50
00:01:55,149 --> 00:01:56,549
I CONFESS I'VE ALWAYS BEEN

51
00:01:56,584 --> 00:01:58,624
SOMETHING
OF AN ARMCHAIR DETECTIVE.

52
00:01:58,652 --> 00:02:00,622
PAUL, YOU COULDN'T POSSIBLY.
THE CHANCELLOR.

53
00:02:00,654 --> 00:02:02,464
I JUST TELL HIM THAT

54
00:02:02,490 --> 00:02:04,060
IT'S A MURDER
INVESTIGATION, RIGHT?

55
00:02:04,091 --> 00:02:05,631
COME ON, DANIEL.

56
00:02:05,659 --> 00:02:07,059
YOU'LL NEED TO KEEP HIM
ENTERTAINED WHILE I'M GONE.

57
00:02:07,094 --> 00:02:08,264
Help me.

58
00:02:08,296 --> 00:02:11,396
WH-- UH, DEAN HALEY, UH,
ACTUALLY,

59
00:02:11,432 --> 00:02:14,032
OUR VICTIM MAY HAVE SUFFERED
SOME HEAD INJURIES,

60
00:02:14,067 --> 00:02:16,797
SO I DO NEED A BRAIN SPECIALIST
TO REVIEW THE X-RAYS.

61
00:02:16,837 --> 00:02:19,737
YOU COULDN'T POSSIBLY SPARE
DANIEL, UH, JUST FOR AN HOUR?

62
00:02:19,773 --> 00:02:23,413
I'M SURE THE CHANCELLOR
WILL UNDERSTAND.

63
00:02:23,444 --> 00:02:26,584
THIS IS VERY EXCITING.

64
00:02:26,614 --> 00:02:28,084
[ RETCHING ]

65
00:02:28,115 --> 00:02:30,075
[ SPITTING ]

66
00:02:30,117 --> 00:02:33,247
OH.
[ SNIFFS ]

67
00:02:33,287 --> 00:02:35,257
PROBABLY A LITTLE
TOO MUCH BUBBLY

68
00:02:35,289 --> 00:02:37,089
AT THE RECEPTION,
I THINK.

69
00:02:37,124 --> 00:02:40,564
OKAY. UM, LET'S SEE
WHAT WE'VE GOT HERE.

70
00:02:40,594 --> 00:02:44,934
WELL, THE ANGEL APPEARS TO DRAW
FROM CHRISTIAN INFLUENCES,

71
00:02:44,965 --> 00:02:48,395
BUT THESE EIGHT WINGS

72
00:02:48,436 --> 00:02:51,406
PROBABLY REPRESENT
THE EIGHT ARMS OF SHIVA,

73
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:53,109
THE HINDU GOD
OF DESTRUCTION.

74
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:54,780
AH. UH-HUH.

75
00:02:54,808 --> 00:02:57,108
WHICH WOULD MAKE
THIS SIMIAN FIGURE

76
00:02:57,144 --> 00:02:59,414
REPRESENTATIVE OF HANUMAN,
THE HINDU MONKEY GOD.

77
00:02:59,447 --> 00:03:02,577
AND I'D SAY THESE NUMBERS
REPRESENT

78
00:03:02,616 --> 00:03:05,786
THE BOOK OF RUTH,
CHAPTER 1, VERSE 16.

79
00:03:05,819 --> 00:03:08,119
"THY PEOPLE
SHALL BE MY PEOPLE."

80
00:03:08,155 --> 00:03:09,655
THE WORDS NAOMI SPOKE

81
00:03:09,690 --> 00:03:11,020
WHEN CONVERTING TO THE FAITH
OF HER MOTHER-IN-LAW.

82
00:03:11,058 --> 00:03:13,588
SO, YOU PROBABLY
WANT TO MAKE INQUIRIES

83
00:03:13,627 --> 00:03:15,297
AT A LOCAL HINDU TEMPLE

84
00:03:15,329 --> 00:03:17,969
FREQUENTED BY CONVERTS FROM
THE JUDEO-CHRISTIAN TRADITION.

85
00:03:17,998 --> 00:03:20,628
YOU MIGHT WANT TO INQUIRE
AT A LOCAL METHADONE CLINIC.

86
00:03:20,668 --> 00:03:22,298
WHY DO YOU SAY THAT?

87
00:03:22,336 --> 00:03:24,636
I THINK IT'S A PRETTY SAFE BET
YOUR VICTIM HERE WAS A JUNKIE.

88
00:03:24,672 --> 00:03:27,312
"MONKEY ON MY BACK," IS A COMMON
TERM FOR HEROIN ADDICTION.

89
00:03:27,341 --> 00:03:30,811
1:16 IS PROBABLY
A SOBRIETY DATE,

90
00:03:30,844 --> 00:03:32,314
WHICH A LOT OF ADDICTS
TATTOO ON THEIR BODIES.

91
00:03:32,346 --> 00:03:33,806
IF HE GOT SOBER
WITH THE HELP OF METHADONE,

92
00:03:33,847 --> 00:03:35,817
MAYBE SOMEBODY AT A CLINIC
WOULD RECOGNIZE HIM.

93
00:03:35,849 --> 00:03:40,219
OF COURSE, I DON'T WANT TO...
CONTRADICT THE EXPERT.

94
00:03:40,254 --> 00:03:42,524
[ RETCHES ]

95
00:03:49,563 --> 00:03:52,333
Kate: I'M HERE ABOUT YOUR SON,
MRS. BAKER.

96
00:03:52,366 --> 00:03:53,766
WHAT'S JARED DONE NOW?

97
00:03:53,801 --> 00:03:56,341
WELL, HE'S LISTED YOU
AS HIS EMERGENCY CONTACT

98
00:03:56,370 --> 00:03:59,370
ON HIS INTAKE FORM AT
THE 7th STREET METHADONE CLINIC.

99
00:04:00,441 --> 00:04:02,511
YOUR SON'S BODY
WAS FOUND YESTERDAY

100
00:04:02,543 --> 00:04:04,043
IN THE FOREST PRESERVE.

101
00:04:04,077 --> 00:04:08,277
IT APPEARS HE WAS MURDERED.
I'M...VERY SORRY.

102
00:04:15,122 --> 00:04:17,892
THANK YOU FOR BRINGING ME
THE NEWS IN PERSON.

103
00:04:21,028 --> 00:04:24,158
I ALWAYS THOUGHT I WOULD GET A
CALL IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

104
00:04:24,197 --> 00:04:26,027
YOU WERE
EXPECTING THIS?

105
00:04:26,066 --> 00:04:27,696
I TRIED EVERYTHING --

106
00:04:27,735 --> 00:04:32,035
THERAPISTS, REHAB,
A CLINIC IN SWITZERLAND.

107
00:04:32,072 --> 00:04:37,882
BUT WHEN HE TURNED 21 AND CAME
INTO HIS GRANDFATHER'S TRUST,

108
00:04:37,911 --> 00:04:42,021
HE HAD MONEY FOR ALL THE DRUGS
HE COULD POSSIBLY DESIRE.

109
00:04:42,049 --> 00:04:45,319
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW HIM?

110
00:04:45,353 --> 00:04:48,123
FOUR MONTHS AGO,
MAYBE FIVE.

111
00:04:48,155 --> 00:04:49,955
OKAY.

112
00:04:49,990 --> 00:04:51,690
AND DO YOU KNOW
WHERE HE WAS LIVING?

113
00:04:51,725 --> 00:04:54,225
WITH SOME KIND
OF RELIGIOUS CULT.

114
00:04:54,261 --> 00:04:57,061
IT BLED HIM
OF EVERY LAST CENT HE HAD LEFT.

115
00:04:57,097 --> 00:05:00,067
[ Voice breaking ] HE SAID
HE FOUND THE VOICE OF GOD

116
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:02,170
AND WAS FINALLY
GETTING CLEAN.

117
00:05:05,072 --> 00:05:08,412
SOME GOOD
THE VOICE OF GOD DID HIM.

118
00:05:08,442 --> 00:05:11,242
Kate:
IT'S CALLED HAVEN HOUSE.

119
00:05:11,278 --> 00:05:13,578
LOOKS LIKE
SOME SORT OF COMMUNE.

120
00:05:13,614 --> 00:05:17,494
IT'S ALL CENTERED AROUND
THIS KID -- KYLE JENSEN.

121
00:05:17,518 --> 00:05:19,718
16 YEARS OLD.

122
00:05:19,753 --> 00:05:21,423
THEY SAY HE TALKS
DIRECTLY TO GOD.

123
00:05:21,455 --> 00:05:24,425
AND YOUR VICTIM GAVE ALL
HIS MONEY TO THIS WACKO CULT?

124
00:05:24,458 --> 00:05:26,088
ALMOST $500,000.

125
00:05:26,126 --> 00:05:27,086
WHAT?!

126
00:05:27,127 --> 00:05:28,627
THAT'S THE WAY IT WORKS.

127
00:05:28,662 --> 00:05:30,432
EVERYONE WHO JOINS
GIVES EVERY DIME THEY HAVE.

128
00:05:30,464 --> 00:05:32,274
[ LAUGHS ]
IT'S A HAVEN, ALL RIGHT --

129
00:05:32,299 --> 00:05:33,999
FOR ANYBODY
WITH MONEY IN THE BANK

130
00:05:34,034 --> 00:05:35,574
AND NO BRAIN
IN THEIR SKULL.

131
00:05:35,603 --> 00:05:38,573
I SWEAR, IT -- IT --
IT -- IT STAGGERS ME.

132
00:05:38,606 --> 00:05:40,066
MILLENNIUM
AFTER MILLENNIUM,

133
00:05:40,107 --> 00:05:42,277
NO MATTER HOW MANY OF THESE
CHARLATANS ARE UNMASKED,

134
00:05:42,309 --> 00:05:44,179
PEOPLE KEEP SHOVELING GOLD
INTO THE POCKETS

135
00:05:44,211 --> 00:05:45,881
OF THE NEXT CROOK
WHO CLAIMS TO SPEAK

136
00:05:45,913 --> 00:05:48,883
IN THE NAME OF SOME NONEXISTENT
SANTA CLAUS IN THE SKY.

137
00:05:48,916 --> 00:05:50,016
IT'S UNBELIEVABLE.

138
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:51,120
I THOUGHT
YOU'D BE INTERESTED.

139
00:05:51,151 --> 00:05:52,191
DO YOU WANT TO
TAG ALONG?

140
00:05:52,219 --> 00:05:53,989
TRY AND STOP ME.

141
00:06:06,634 --> 00:06:07,774
[ ALARM CHIRPS ]

142
00:06:07,801 --> 00:06:11,271
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

143
00:06:11,304 --> 00:06:14,814
HI. ARE YOU HERE
FOR KYLE?

144
00:06:14,842 --> 00:06:16,642
HE'LL BE TALKING TO EVERYBODY
IN JUST A COUPLE OF MINUTES.

145
00:06:16,677 --> 00:06:18,547
WE'RE WITH THE FBI.

146
00:06:18,579 --> 00:06:21,479
THE FBI?
IS THERE SOMETHING WRONG?

147
00:06:21,515 --> 00:06:23,315
WE'D LIKE TO TALK
TO WHOEVER'S IN CHARGE.

148
00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:25,820
WELL, NOBODY'S
REALLY IN CHARGE.

149
00:06:25,853 --> 00:06:27,293
UM, THIS IS
TOM AND SANDY'S HOUSE,

150
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:28,820
BUT THEY'RE IN
WITH KYLE RIGHT NOW.

151
00:06:28,856 --> 00:06:31,386
COULD THIS WAIT
TILL HE'S FINISHED?

152
00:06:31,425 --> 00:06:33,325
H-HE REALLY LIKES TO TELL US
WHAT GOD SAID TO HIM

153
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,830
WHILE IT'S STILL FRESH
IN HIS HEAD.

154
00:06:34,862 --> 00:06:37,002
ANY CHANCE
WE COULD LISTEN

155
00:06:37,030 --> 00:06:38,670
TO THE WORD OF GOD
WHILE WE WAIT?

156
00:06:38,699 --> 00:06:40,869
EVERYONE IS WELCOME.

157
00:06:42,470 --> 00:06:45,570
Behave yourself,
Daniel.

158
00:06:45,606 --> 00:06:48,406
Tom: IT'S WONDERFUL
TO SEE ALL OF YOU HERE.

159
00:06:48,442 --> 00:06:50,582
SO MANY NEW FACES
HERE TODAY.

160
00:06:50,611 --> 00:06:53,081
I'M TOM SHELBY, AND, UH,
THIS IS MY WIFE, SANDY.

161
00:06:53,113 --> 00:06:55,183
HI, EVERYBODY.

162
00:06:55,215 --> 00:06:57,245
AND, UH,
THESE ARE THE TWO BOYS

163
00:06:57,284 --> 00:06:59,554
I WAS LUCKY ENOUGH
TO GET IN THE PACKAGE DEAL

164
00:06:59,587 --> 00:07:00,687
WHEN I MARRIED HER...

165
00:07:00,721 --> 00:07:03,191
...GREG AND KYLE.

166
00:07:03,223 --> 00:07:06,033
UH, NOW, AS MUCH AS I'D LIKE
TO BELIEVE OTHERWISE,

167
00:07:06,059 --> 00:07:08,699
I KNOW YOU DIDN'T COME
TO HEAR ME FLAP MY JAW,

168
00:07:08,729 --> 00:07:11,699
SO I'M GONNA SHUT UP
AND TURN THE FLOOR OVER TO KYLE.

169
00:07:11,732 --> 00:07:13,932
[ APPLAUSE ]

170
00:07:16,504 --> 00:07:17,844
THANKS, TOM.

171
00:07:17,871 --> 00:07:21,481
UM...GOD PICKS
THE CRAZIEST TIMES

172
00:07:21,509 --> 00:07:24,039
TO TAP ME ON THE SHOULDER
AND START TALKING.

173
00:07:24,077 --> 00:07:25,377
TODAY, IT WAS WHILE
I WAS DOING THE DISHES,

174
00:07:25,412 --> 00:07:26,882
AND I WANT TO APOLOGIZE
TO MY MOM

175
00:07:26,914 --> 00:07:29,724
FOR THE PITCHER I DROPPED
WHEN I CHECKED OUT.

176
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,050
[ LAUGHTER ]

177
00:07:31,084 --> 00:07:33,924
TODAY, GOD TALKED TO ME
ABOUT DOUBT

178
00:07:33,954 --> 00:07:37,094
AND HOW IMPORTANT IT IS
FOR US NOT TO BE SCARED OF IT.

179
00:07:37,124 --> 00:07:39,094
HE SAID HE GAVE US DOUBT
SO THAT WE'D ALWAYS

180
00:07:39,126 --> 00:07:41,596
BE TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
HOW THINGS REALLY WORK,

181
00:07:41,629 --> 00:07:43,299
YOU KNOW, AND HOW WE CAN
MAKE THEM BETTER.

182
00:07:43,330 --> 00:07:47,740
NOW, THERE ARE PEOPLE
IN THIS ROOM WHO HAVE NO DOUBT,

183
00:07:47,768 --> 00:07:50,068
AND THAT IS
A BEAUTIFUL THING.

184
00:07:50,103 --> 00:07:51,713
BUT GOD ALSO TALKED TO ME

185
00:07:51,739 --> 00:07:54,679
ABOUT HOW BEING TOO SURE
OF ANYTHING CAN BE DANGEROUS.

186
00:07:56,276 --> 00:08:00,406
AND THERE IS SOMEBODY HERE
WHO HAS ONLY DOUBT...

187
00:08:00,447 --> 00:08:03,517
WHO DOESN'T BELIEVE
AT ALL.

188
00:08:05,853 --> 00:08:09,493
BUT I'M REALLY GLAD
HE'S HERE.

189
00:08:22,970 --> 00:08:24,500
[ SANDY SIGHS ]

190
00:08:24,538 --> 00:08:27,838
JARED WAS SUCH
A BEAUTIFUL PERSON.

191
00:08:27,875 --> 00:08:29,605
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW HIM?

192
00:08:29,643 --> 00:08:32,613
ABOUT 6:00
JUST YESTERDAY MORNING.

193
00:08:32,646 --> 00:08:34,846
HE -- HE WENT OUT
ON HIS JOG.

194
00:08:34,882 --> 00:08:37,952
AND YOU DIDN'T WONDER WHY HE
DIDN'T COME HOME LAST NIGHT?

195
00:08:37,985 --> 00:08:39,845
NO. EVERYBODY HERE
IS FREE TO COME AND GO.

196
00:08:39,887 --> 00:08:42,957
Nikki:
I WAS WORRIED, ACTUALLY.

197
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:44,960
HE SAID HE'D BEEN SEEING
HIS OLD FRIENDS FROM K-TOWN,

198
00:08:44,992 --> 00:08:46,462
WHERE HE USED TO SCORE.

199
00:08:46,493 --> 00:08:49,703
I-I WAS SCARED THAT HE MIGHT BE
GOING BACK TO DRUGS.

200
00:08:49,730 --> 00:08:53,300
DID HE MENTION ANY OF THESE
OLD FRIENDS BY NAME?

201
00:08:53,333 --> 00:08:54,973
NO.

202
00:08:55,002 --> 00:08:56,202
SHANE.

203
00:08:56,236 --> 00:08:58,206
[ SIGHS ]
SHANE FLANNERY.

204
00:08:58,238 --> 00:09:00,038
UM [CLEARS THROAT]
HE USED TO LIVE HERE.

205
00:09:00,073 --> 00:09:02,783
WELL, TURNED OUT,
HE WAS KIND OF A FANATIC.

206
00:09:02,810 --> 00:09:06,050
HE DIDN'T THINK WE WERE DOING
ENOUGH TO PROTECT KYLE.

207
00:09:06,079 --> 00:09:09,649
HE THOUGHT WE WERE LETTING IN
THE SCUM OF THE EARTH --

208
00:09:09,683 --> 00:09:11,453
ADDICTS AND PROSTITUTES
AND ALL KINDS OF SINNERS.

209
00:09:11,484 --> 00:09:13,324
THAT'S WHO COMES
IN NEED OF GOD'S HEALING.

210
00:09:13,353 --> 00:09:15,593
SHANE THREATENED TO BURN US
ALL ALIVE IN THE HOUSE.

211
00:09:15,623 --> 00:09:17,663
JARED ASKED HIM TO LEAVE,
AND WHEN HE REFUSED,

212
00:09:17,691 --> 00:09:19,991
JARED THREW HIM OUT.

213
00:09:20,027 --> 00:09:21,357
YEAH, AND WHEN HE LEFT,

214
00:09:21,394 --> 00:09:24,004
HE WAS RANTING ABOUT JARED
PAYING FOR HIS SINS.

215
00:09:24,031 --> 00:09:26,731
OKAY. WELL,
WE'LL CERTAINLY LOOK INTO IT.

216
00:09:26,767 --> 00:09:29,167
JARED BAKER SIGNED OVER
HIS ENTIRE TRUST FUND TO YOU.

217
00:09:29,202 --> 00:09:30,502
HALF A MILLION DOLLARS.

218
00:09:30,537 --> 00:09:32,237
WHAT'D YOU DO
WITH THE MONEY?

219
00:09:32,272 --> 00:09:34,112
EVERYTHING WE TAKE IN
GOES TO THE SHELTER,

220
00:09:34,141 --> 00:09:36,081
THE FOOD BANK,
OR THE SCHOOL IN AFGHANISTAN.

221
00:09:36,109 --> 00:09:39,749
DID JARED EVER QUESTION HOW YOU
WERE SPENDING HIS INHERITANCE?

222
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:41,480
I-I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE INSINUATING.

223
00:09:41,514 --> 00:09:43,754
IF YOU'RE IMPLYING THAT WE HAD
SOMETHING TO DO WITH --

224
00:09:43,784 --> 00:09:46,424
TOM, IT'S OKAY.

225
00:09:46,453 --> 00:09:47,823
PEOPLE GIVE US THEIR MONEY

226
00:09:47,855 --> 00:09:50,085
BECAUSE OF THE FIRST THING
GOD EVER SAID TO ME.

227
00:09:50,123 --> 00:09:53,993
"I ONLY ASK FOR ONE THING --
EVERYTHING.

228
00:09:54,027 --> 00:09:57,127
BUT IN EXCHANGE,
I GIVE EVERYTHING."

229
00:09:57,164 --> 00:09:59,534
Nikki:
I CAME HERE WITH NOTHING --

230
00:09:59,566 --> 00:10:01,526
JUST A COKE HABIT
AND A LOT OF FEAR --

231
00:10:01,568 --> 00:10:04,938
AND THESE PEOPLE TOOK ME IN
LIKE A DAUGHTER.

232
00:10:04,972 --> 00:10:07,042
AND GOD KEPT HIS PROMISE.

233
00:10:07,074 --> 00:10:09,214
HE GAVE ME EVERYTHING.

234
00:10:09,242 --> 00:10:12,552
EVEN THE MAN
THAT I'M GOING TO MARRY.

235
00:10:12,579 --> 00:10:14,549
Tom: YOU NEED TO
FIND SHANE FLANNERY.

236
00:10:14,581 --> 00:10:17,751
IF HE DID KILL JARED BAKER,
HE MIGHT KILL SOMEBODY ELSE.

237
00:10:23,757 --> 00:10:25,727
Kate: YES.
SHANE FLANNERY.

238
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:27,899
UH-HUH. I'M E-MAILING A PHOTO
AND A DESCRIPTION.

239
00:10:27,928 --> 00:10:30,228
I WANT EVERY MAN ON IT
WE CAN SPARE.

240
00:10:30,263 --> 00:10:32,073
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

241
00:10:32,099 --> 00:10:34,569
I'M GONNA STICK AROUND.
I WANT TO TALK TO KYLE.

242
00:10:34,601 --> 00:10:36,901
ABOUT WHAT?

243
00:10:36,937 --> 00:10:39,307
I'M JUST CURIOUS
ABOUT SOMETHING.

244
00:10:42,609 --> 00:10:44,039
KYLE?

245
00:10:44,077 --> 00:10:45,747
DO YOU HAVE A MINUTE?

246
00:10:45,779 --> 00:10:49,649
SURE.

247
00:10:51,518 --> 00:10:54,048
HOW DID YOU KNOW
THAT I WAS A NONBELIEVER?

248
00:10:54,087 --> 00:10:55,817
DID, UH,
GOD TELL YOU THAT?

249
00:10:55,856 --> 00:10:57,316
[ CHUCKLES ]

250
00:10:57,357 --> 00:10:59,887
I COULD JUST SEE IT
IN YOUR FACE.

251
00:10:59,927 --> 00:11:03,697
IT TAKES WORK NOT TO BELIEVE
IN GOD, AND THE EFFORT SHOWS.

252
00:11:03,731 --> 00:11:05,301
I THINK IT TAKES
A LOT MORE EFFORT

253
00:11:05,332 --> 00:11:07,102
TO BELIEVE IN SOMETHING
YOU CAN'T SEE.

254
00:11:07,134 --> 00:11:08,344
ARE YOU KIDDING?

255
00:11:13,941 --> 00:11:16,911
HOW COULD ANYBODY LOOK
AT SOMETHING SO PERFECT

256
00:11:16,944 --> 00:11:18,184
AND BEAUTIFUL AND DELICIOUS

257
00:11:18,211 --> 00:11:20,451
AND THINK THAT IT GOT THAT WAY
BY ACCIDENT?

258
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,280
WELL, THERE'S A SCIENTIFIC
ANSWER TO THAT, KYLE.

259
00:11:22,315 --> 00:11:23,645
EARLIER VERSIONS
OF THE RASPBERRY

260
00:11:23,683 --> 00:11:25,093
WEREN'T SO BEAUTIFUL
AND DELICIOUS,

261
00:11:25,118 --> 00:11:26,818
SO THEY COULDN'T ATTRACT
ENOUGH BIRDS

262
00:11:26,854 --> 00:11:29,024
TO SPREAD THEIR SEEDS
AROUND.

263
00:11:29,056 --> 00:11:32,026
I KNOW HOW EVOLUTION WORKS.
I LOVE DARWIN.

264
00:11:32,059 --> 00:11:33,789
HE WAS THE FIRST PERSON
IN HISTORY

265
00:11:33,827 --> 00:11:35,227
TO LOOK BEHIND THE CURTAIN

266
00:11:35,262 --> 00:11:37,702
AND SEE HOW GOD
ACTUALLY MAKES IT ALL WORK.

267
00:11:39,332 --> 00:11:43,472
WHEN DID GOD
FIRST START TALKING TO YOU?

268
00:11:43,503 --> 00:11:46,973
[ CHUCKLES ]
WHEN I WAS 12.

269
00:11:47,007 --> 00:11:48,437
BUT YOU'RE NOT FOOLING ME.

270
00:11:48,475 --> 00:11:49,875
I KNOW YOU THINK
I'M EITHER TOTALLY FULL OF IT

271
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,540
OR JUST PLAIN CRAZY.

272
00:11:51,578 --> 00:11:53,648
AND SO DID MY PARENTS,
AT FIRST.

273
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:58,190
W-WHAT DOES IT FEEL LIKE WHEN
YOU'RE HEARING GOD'S VOICE?

274
00:12:00,253 --> 00:12:02,893
IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

275
00:12:02,923 --> 00:12:04,833
EVERYTHING
KIND OF DISAPPEARS.

276
00:12:04,858 --> 00:12:07,758
IT'S LIKE I'M ASLEEP AND AWAKE
AT THE SAME TIME.

277
00:12:07,795 --> 00:12:10,195
DO YOU GET HEADACHES
WHEN THAT HAPPENS?

278
00:12:10,230 --> 00:12:11,230
FEEL NAUSEATED?

279
00:12:11,264 --> 00:12:12,504
YEAH.
HOW DID YOU KNOW?

280
00:12:12,532 --> 00:12:15,472
JUST A HUNCH.

281
00:12:15,502 --> 00:12:18,142
WELL, ANYWAY,
IT'S TOTALLY WORTH IT

282
00:12:18,171 --> 00:12:21,981
'CAUSE I ALSO GET THIS AMAZING,
LIKE, EUPHORIA.

283
00:12:22,009 --> 00:12:23,639
HMM.

284
00:12:23,676 --> 00:12:27,146
HEADACHES, NAUSEA,
EUPHORIA, VOICES --

285
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:30,680
THESE ARE CLASSIC SYMPTOMS
OF TEMPORAL LOBE EPILEPSY,

286
00:12:30,717 --> 00:12:32,087
WHICH COULD BE CAUSED
BY A TUMOR.

287
00:12:32,119 --> 00:12:33,419
I-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

288
00:12:33,453 --> 00:12:35,263
HE HAS A CHECK-UP
EVERY YEAR,

289
00:12:35,288 --> 00:12:36,988
AND HIS DOCTOR
HAS NEVER SAID ANYTHING.

290
00:12:37,024 --> 00:12:38,694
DID YOU EVER TAKE HIM
TO A NEUROLOGIST?

291
00:12:38,725 --> 00:12:40,525
THERE WAS NO REASON TO.
HE'S IN PERFECT HEALTH.

292
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:43,160
I'M SORRY, BUT HE'S NOT.

293
00:12:43,196 --> 00:12:44,696
THIS KIND OF TUMOR

294
00:12:44,731 --> 00:12:46,431
CAN ALSO PRESS ON NEIGHBORING
AREAS OF THE BRAIN.

295
00:12:46,466 --> 00:12:49,196
IT CAN BE LIFE-THREATENING
IF IT'S NOT TREATED,

296
00:12:49,236 --> 00:12:51,196
OF KYLE COULD HAVE A SEIZURE
WHILE HE'S DRIVING.

297
00:12:51,238 --> 00:12:52,768
I'D LIKE TO BRING HIM IN
FOR SOME TESTS.

298
00:12:52,806 --> 00:12:54,506
AND IF THEY SHOW
WHAT I THINK THEY'LL SHOW,

299
00:12:54,541 --> 00:12:55,911
HE MAY NEED SURGERY.

300
00:12:55,943 --> 00:12:57,783
WELL, I-I COULD BRING HIM IN
TOMORROW WHEN --

301
00:12:57,811 --> 00:12:59,011
Kyle: MOM, WAIT.

302
00:12:59,046 --> 00:13:01,176
ARE YOU SAYING THIS CONDITION

303
00:13:01,214 --> 00:13:03,384
IS WHAT'S MAKING ME
HEAR GOD'S VOICE?

304
00:13:03,416 --> 00:13:05,716
IT'S NOT GOD, KYLE.

305
00:13:05,752 --> 00:13:07,552
IT'S A NEUROLOGICAL
ABNORMALITY.

306
00:13:07,587 --> 00:13:09,717
WELL, IF IT IS,
GOD MUST HAVE GIVEN IT TO ME

307
00:13:09,756 --> 00:13:11,216
SO HE COULD HAVE A WAY
TO TALK TO ME.

308
00:13:11,258 --> 00:13:12,388
I'M NOT GETTING RID OF IT.

309
00:13:12,425 --> 00:13:15,125
THIS COULD BE
A FATAL CONDITION.

310
00:13:15,162 --> 00:13:16,732
BEING ALIVE
IS A FATAL CONDITION.

311
00:13:16,763 --> 00:13:18,703
I'M NOT DOING IT, MOM.

312
00:13:18,731 --> 00:13:21,701
MRS. SHELBY, I UNDERSTAND KYLE'S
COMMITMENT TO HIS BELIEFS,

313
00:13:21,734 --> 00:13:23,074
BUT HE IS STILL A MINOR.

314
00:13:23,103 --> 00:13:25,143
YOU CAN COMPEL HIM
TO GET TREATMENT.

315
00:13:25,172 --> 00:13:27,412
DR. PIERCE, WE'LL DISCUSS
WHAT YOU'VE SAID.

316
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,210
WE'LL TALK TO KYLE
ABOUT IT.

317
00:13:29,242 --> 00:13:31,742
BUT WE ARE NOT GONNA FORCE HIM
TO DO ANYTHING AGAINST HIS WILL.

318
00:13:44,791 --> 00:13:46,431
Daniel:
THIS IS CHILD ABUSE!

319
00:13:46,459 --> 00:13:47,929
THEY'RE NOT FORCING HIM
TO GET TESTED

320
00:13:47,961 --> 00:13:49,131
BECAUSE THEY DON'T WANT
THE GOOSE

321
00:13:49,162 --> 00:13:50,732
TO STOP LAYING
THE GOLDEN EGGS.

322
00:13:50,763 --> 00:13:52,373
[ Chuckling ] IT'S WHAT I'VE
ALWAYS SAID -- RELIGION.

323
00:13:52,399 --> 00:13:54,329
AND, YOU KNOW, IF IT'S NOT
ABOUT BLOOD OR OPPRESSION,

324
00:13:54,367 --> 00:13:55,997
IT'S ABOUT MONEY
IN THE BANK.

325
00:13:56,036 --> 00:13:58,336
THAT IS A GROSS
GENERALIZATION,

326
00:13:58,371 --> 00:14:00,671
NOT TO MENTION
TOTALLY OFFENSIVE.

327
00:14:00,707 --> 00:14:03,177
I MEAN, WHAT ABOUT
THE DALAI LAMA OR --

328
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:04,680
OR MARTIN LUTHER KING?

329
00:14:04,711 --> 00:14:07,681
OR THE INQUISITION
OR 9/11 OR GIORDANO BRUNO?

330
00:14:07,714 --> 00:14:10,354
OH, THEY DIDN'T TEACH YOU
ABOUT HIM IN SUNDAY SCHOOL?

331
00:14:10,383 --> 00:14:14,023
1592 -- GIORDANO BRUNO
MAKES THE WILD, SATANIC CLAIM

332
00:14:14,054 --> 00:14:15,864
THAT THE EARTH
REVOLVES AROUND THE SUN,

333
00:14:15,889 --> 00:14:17,689
SO THE HOLY FATHERS
PRAY TO GOD

334
00:14:17,724 --> 00:14:19,534
AND ARE TOLD THAT
THIS WICKED MAN MUST DIE.

335
00:14:19,559 --> 00:14:22,529
THEY CLAMP HIS TONGUE
TO THE ROOF OF HIS MOUTH,

336
00:14:22,562 --> 00:14:23,832
AND THEY BURN HIM ALIVE,

337
00:14:23,863 --> 00:14:24,973
WHICH MUST HAVE BEEN
THE RIGHT THING TO DO

338
00:14:24,998 --> 00:14:26,298
'CAUSE GOD TOLD THEM
TO DO IT.

339
00:14:26,333 --> 00:14:28,273
LOOK, YES,
THAT IS A HORRIBLE STORY,

340
00:14:28,301 --> 00:14:30,641
BUT HAVEN HOUSE
ISN'T BURNING PEOPLE ALIVE.

341
00:14:30,670 --> 00:14:32,370
YOU MADE A SNAP DIAGNOSIS

342
00:14:32,405 --> 00:14:34,205
AFTER TALKING TO THAT KID
FOR FIVE MINUTES.

343
00:14:34,241 --> 00:14:35,911
YOU DON'T THINK THAT
THAT MIGHT BE

344
00:14:35,943 --> 00:14:37,843
YOUR PREJUDICE
AGAINST RELIGION TALKING?

345
00:14:37,877 --> 00:14:39,847
I-I DIDN'T MAKE
THE CONDITION UP.

346
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:41,509
IT'S WHAT
JOAN WHAT?C HAD.

347
00:14:41,548 --> 00:14:43,678
JOAN OF ARC HAD
TEMPORAL LOBE EPILEPSY.

348
00:14:43,716 --> 00:14:46,016
IT'S WHY SHE THOUGHT
THAT ANGELS WERE TALKING TO HER.

349
00:14:46,053 --> 00:14:47,853
OH, DID YOU EXAMINE HER,
TOO?

350
00:14:47,887 --> 00:14:49,917
IT'S THE CONCLUSION
OF MEDICAL HISTORIANS

351
00:14:49,957 --> 00:14:52,127
BASED ON HER DESCRIPTION
OF HER OWN EXPERIENCE.

352
00:14:52,159 --> 00:14:53,829
AND WE ALL KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED TO HER.

353
00:14:53,860 --> 00:14:56,800
YES. SHE BECAME A GREAT LEADER.
SHE LIBERATED FRANCE.

354
00:14:56,829 --> 00:14:59,069
SHE WAS BURNED AT THE STAKE
AT AGE 19.

355
00:14:59,099 --> 00:15:02,569
SHE WAS A DELUDED GIRL WHOSE
ILLNESS LED TO HER DISASTER.

356
00:15:02,602 --> 00:15:04,302
SHE WAS A HERO.

357
00:15:04,337 --> 00:15:07,237
AT A TIME WHEN WOMEN HAD
LESS POWER THAN FARM ANIMALS,

358
00:15:07,274 --> 00:15:08,744
SHE LED AN ARMY.

359
00:15:08,775 --> 00:15:10,375
I USED TO CARRY HER MEDAL
WHEN I WAS A KID,

360
00:15:10,410 --> 00:15:13,150
AND I STILL LIGHT CANDLES
IN CHURCH FOR HER ON SUNDAY.

361
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:15,150
YOUYES, DANIEL, I DO.H?

362
00:15:15,182 --> 00:15:17,322
AND I PRAY, TOO,
IF YOU WANT TO KNOW.

363
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:18,420
WHY?

364
00:15:18,451 --> 00:15:20,321
BECAUSE I BELIEVE
IN GOD.

365
00:15:20,353 --> 00:15:22,663
IT COMFORTS ME TO TALK TO HIM
ABOUT MY PROBLEMS.

366
00:15:22,689 --> 00:15:25,329
AND DOES HE ANSWER YOU BACK
LIKE HE DOES WITH KYLE?

367
00:15:25,358 --> 00:15:26,958
OKAY.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

368
00:15:26,994 --> 00:15:29,164
I DO NOT HAVE TIME TO GET INTO
A THEOLOGICAL DEBATE WITH YOU.

369
00:15:29,196 --> 00:15:30,726
I NEED TO FIND
SHANE FLANNERY.

370
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:32,773
WHICH IS EXACTLY WHAT
OUR FRIENDS AT HAVEN HOUSE

371
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:34,029
WANT YOU TO BE DOING.

372
00:15:34,067 --> 00:15:36,037
HOW DO YOU KNOW
THAT JARED BAKER

373
00:15:36,069 --> 00:15:37,769
DIDN'T JUST GET
[BLEEP] OFF ONE DAY

374
00:15:37,804 --> 00:15:39,844
THAT HIS ENTIRE TRUST FUND
WAS GOING INTO THEIR POCKETS,

375
00:15:39,872 --> 00:15:42,042
SO HE TRIED TO GET IT BACK,
AND THEY OFFED HIM FOR IT?

376
00:15:42,075 --> 00:15:44,605
BECAUSE THE I.R.S.
IS ALL OVER PLACES LIKE THAT.

377
00:15:44,644 --> 00:15:46,384
OH, AND NOTHING
EVER GETS PAST UNCLE SAM.

378
00:15:46,413 --> 00:15:48,853
ALL RIGHT, FINE, IF IT WOULD
MAKE YOU FEEL BETTER,

379
00:15:48,881 --> 00:15:50,681
I WILL PUT IN A CALL
TO THE I.R.S.,

380
00:15:50,717 --> 00:15:52,717
BUT MY MONEY IS ON SHANE.

381
00:15:56,923 --> 00:15:59,133
Ethan: I WAS EXACTLY
WHERE YOU ARE, DR. PIERCE.

382
00:15:59,159 --> 00:16:01,089
I WAS POSITIVE A PLACE RAKING IN
THAT KIND OF CASH

383
00:16:01,128 --> 00:16:02,758
HAD TO BE A SCAM,

384
00:16:02,795 --> 00:16:04,395
BUT I'VE BEEN TEARING
THEIR BOOKS APART AT THE SEAMS

385
00:16:04,431 --> 00:16:06,401
FOR TWO YEARS, AND I GOT TO
TELL YOU, IT'S LEGIT.

386
00:16:06,433 --> 00:16:07,903
WE'RE TALKING
ABOUT MILLIONS OF DOLLARS.

387
00:16:07,934 --> 00:16:09,404
WHERE IS IT ALL GOING?

388
00:16:09,436 --> 00:16:11,396
WELL, ABOUT 2% GOES
TO ADMINISTRATIVE EXPENSES,

389
00:16:11,438 --> 00:16:13,508
WHICH IS AS LOW AS IT GETS
IN NONPROFIT-LAND,

390
00:16:13,540 --> 00:16:15,710
AND SOME GOES
TO LOCAL CHARITIES --

391
00:16:15,742 --> 00:16:17,912
FOOD BANK, MEALS ON WHEELS,
SHELTER.

392
00:16:17,944 --> 00:16:20,314
BIGGEST CHUNK GOES
TO THE SCHOOL IN AFGHANISTAN.

393
00:16:20,347 --> 00:16:21,607
[ CELLMORETTI.NGS ]

394
00:16:21,648 --> 00:16:22,978
ISN'T IT POSSIBLE
THEY'RE FOOLING YOU?

395
00:16:23,016 --> 00:16:24,476
THAT -- THAT
THEY'RE COOKING THE BOOKS?

396
00:16:24,517 --> 00:16:26,747
I'D LIKE TO THINK,
AFTER 20 YEARS IN THIS PLACE,

397
00:16:26,786 --> 00:16:28,256
THAT I'M A PRETTY HARD GUY
TO FOOL.

398
00:16:28,288 --> 00:16:29,288
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

399
00:16:29,322 --> 00:16:31,922
CPD JUST FOUND
OUR SUSPECT.

400
00:16:31,958 --> 00:16:34,428
THANK YOU.

401
00:16:34,461 --> 00:16:36,101
Kate: MR. FLANNERY,

402
00:16:36,129 --> 00:16:38,769
DID YOU THREATEN
TO BURN DOWN HAVEN HOUSE,

403
00:16:38,798 --> 00:16:40,428
SEND ALL ITS RESIDENTS
TO HELL?

404
00:16:40,467 --> 00:16:42,237
I SPOKE THE TRUTH.

405
00:16:42,269 --> 00:16:45,439
I SAID THAT GOD WOULD BRING
THE FIRE OF HIS VENGEANCE

406
00:16:45,472 --> 00:16:47,412
DOWN ON THAT HOUSE.

407
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:50,240
DID YOU SPECIFICALLY THREATEN
TO KILL JARED BAKER?

408
00:16:50,277 --> 00:16:53,507
IT WAS GOD WHO DELIVERED
HIS JUDGMENT ON THAT HERETIC.

409
00:16:53,546 --> 00:16:55,616
OKAY. WHERE WERE YOU
LAST TUESDAY MORNING?

410
00:16:55,648 --> 00:16:57,178
ACROSS THE STREET
FROM HAVEN HOUSE,

411
00:16:57,217 --> 00:16:58,947
GUARDING THE CHOSEN ONE --
I WAS THERE ALL NIGHT.

412
00:16:58,985 --> 00:17:00,685
CAN ANYONE VERIFY THAT?

413
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:03,920
ONLY GOD, WHO WILL PURIFY
ALL THE SINNERS IN THAT HOUSE

414
00:17:03,956 --> 00:17:05,956
WITH THE FIRES
OF HIS VENGEANCE...

415
00:17:05,992 --> 00:17:09,532
STARTING WITH THOSE WHO TRAMPLE
ON THE SEVENTH COMMANDMENT.

416
00:17:09,562 --> 00:17:11,832
OKAY, I'M A LITTLE RUSTY
ON MY COMMANDMENTS,

417
00:17:11,864 --> 00:17:14,334
BUT I THINK I REMEMBER
WHICH ONE THE SEVENTH IS.

418
00:17:14,367 --> 00:17:16,767
NOW, WHO IN THE HOUSE
WAS COMMITTING ADULTERY?

419
00:17:16,803 --> 00:17:18,613
THAT LYING [BLEEP]
NIKKI.

420
00:17:19,572 --> 00:17:21,472
SHE'S ENGAGED
TO KYLE'S BROTHER,

421
00:17:21,508 --> 00:17:24,708
SO WHY WAS SHE RUTTING
LIKE A SOW WITH THE DEAD MAN?

422
00:17:24,744 --> 00:17:26,654
OKAY, SO, YOU'RE SAYING

423
00:17:26,679 --> 00:17:30,479
NIKKI WAS RUTTING LIKE A SOW
WITH JARED BAKER?

424
00:17:30,517 --> 00:17:32,317
IT WAS AFTER MIDNIGHT.

425
00:17:32,352 --> 00:17:34,592
I SAW THE LIGHT GO ON
IN HIS WINDOW.

426
00:17:34,621 --> 00:17:38,061
SHE CAME INTO HIS ROOM
AND TOOK HIM IN HER ARMS.

427
00:17:38,091 --> 00:17:40,891
MAYBE KYLE'S BROTHER
SAW WHAT I SAW.

428
00:17:40,927 --> 00:17:44,157
MAYBE GOD ENTRUSTED HIM
WITH THE FIRE OF HIS VENGEANCE.

429
00:17:44,197 --> 00:17:46,527
[ French accent ]
HE IS NOT THE KILLER.

430
00:17:49,001 --> 00:17:50,601
HAVE YOU EVER MET
A HOLY WARRIOR

431
00:17:50,637 --> 00:17:52,667
WHO SHOT HIS VICTIM
IN THE BACK?

432
00:17:52,705 --> 00:17:55,505
NORMALLY, THEY BURN
THEIR VICTIMS OR CRUCIFY THEM

433
00:17:55,542 --> 00:17:57,512
OR RITUALLY DRAIN
THEIR BLOOD.

434
00:17:57,544 --> 00:18:00,314
SHE'S CHASING
THE WRONG CAT.

435
00:18:00,347 --> 00:18:03,847
I WAS SENT TO HELP YOU
CATCH THE RIGHT ONE.

436
00:18:03,883 --> 00:18:06,753
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "SENT"?
WHO SENT YOU?

437
00:18:06,786 --> 00:18:08,656
GOD, OF COURSE.

