00:18:10,557 --> 00:18:13,187
MESSENGER OF GOD.

439
00:18:13,226 --> 00:18:14,856
FRENCH ACCENT.

440
00:18:14,894 --> 00:18:17,104
LATE MEDIEVAL,
HOMESPUN TUNIC.

441
00:18:17,130 --> 00:18:19,030
GREAT.

442
00:18:19,065 --> 00:18:21,525
