449
00:18:43,156 --> 00:18:44,416
AT 2:00 IN THE MORNING?

450
00:18:44,457 --> 00:18:46,227
MY ROOM IS
RIGHT NEXT DOOR TO HIS.

451
00:18:46,259 --> 00:18:47,929
