I HEARD HIM CRYING.

452
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:50,460
I WAS WORRIED, SO I WENT
AND KNOCKED ON HIS DOOR.

453
00:18:50,497 --> 00:18:51,857
DO YOU THINK
THAT YOUR FIANCé

454
00:18:51,898 --> 00:18:53,598
MIGHT HAVE SEEN YOU
KNOCK ON HIS DOOR?

455
00:18:53,633 --> 00:18:56,373
NO. GREG -- GREG'S ROOM
IS DOWNSTAIRS IN THE BACK.

456
00:18:56,403 --> 00:18:58,873
JARED WAS
IN A TERRIBLE STATE.

457
00:18:58,905 --> 00:19:01,535
HE TOLD ME HE HAD BEEN
SEEING HIS FRIENDS IN K-TOWN

458
00:19:01,574 --> 00:19:03,644
AND THAT HE WAS WORRIED
HE MIGHT SLIP.

459
00:19:03,676 --> 00:19:07,146
