AND MADE A PASS AT ME.

461
00:19:10,016 --> 00:19:11,476
I TOLD HIM
I WOULD NEVER BETRAY GREG,

462
00:19:11,518 --> 00:19:12,948
AND I WENT BACK
TO MY ROOM.

463
00:19:12,985 --> 00:19:15,655
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL US
ANY OF THIS BEFORE?

464
00:19:15,688 --> 00:19:18,328
I TOLD YOU THAT I THOUGHT
JARED WAS HAVING A ROUGH TIME.

465
00:19:18,358 --> 00:19:22,628
I DIDN'T TELL YOU THE REST
BECAUSE GREG LOVED JARED.

466
00:19:22,662 --> 00:19:25,672
IT WOULD HAVE ONLY UPSET HIM,
AND FOR WHAT?

467
00:19:31,037 --> 00:19:34,167
HEY.
I HEARD YOU GUYS WERE BACK.

468
00:19:34,207 --> 00:19:35,837
DID YKate: YES.ANE?

469
00:19:35,875 --> 00:19:37,675
BUT WE DON'T THINK
HDANIEL.T.

