471
00:19:42,215 --> 00:19:45,585
WELL, WHAT WERE YOU
TALKING TO NIKKI ABOUT?

472
00:19:45,618 --> 00:19:47,088
DOES SHE KNOW
SOMETHING?

473
00:19:47,119 --> 00:19:48,319
KYLE, I --

474
00:19:48,355 --> 00:19:49,785
OKAY.

475
00:19:49,822 --> 00:19:53,092
