TO YOU FOR A MINUTE?

476
00:19:53,125 --> 00:19:54,485
NOT ABOUT THE CASE.

477
00:19:54,527 --> 00:19:56,857
I'LL BE IN THE CAR.

478
00:19:58,865 --> 00:20:01,195
WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND?

479
