480
00:20:06,072 --> 00:20:08,642
GOD TOLD ME I WASN'T
GONNA BE ALIVE FOR VERY LONG.

481
00:20:10,042 --> 00:20:12,952
I GUESS HE'S SAYING
THE SAME THING YOU ARE.

482
00:20:12,979 --> 00:20:15,619
YOU KNOW I DON'T BELIEVE
IN GOD, KYLE.

483
00:20:15,648 --> 00:20:18,318
