TELLING YOU YOU'RE NOT WELL,

484
00:20:18,351 --> 00:20:20,521
YOU SHOULD LISTEN TO IT
AND GET TREATMENT.

485
00:20:20,553 --> 00:20:22,623
I'M NOT DOING THAT.

486
00:20:22,655 --> 00:20:25,055
I JUST WANT TO KNOW
HOW LONG I HAVE

487
00:20:25,091 --> 00:20:28,631
SO I CAN,
YOU KNOW, MAKE PLANS.

488
00:20:28,661 --> 00:20:30,761
YOUR CONDITION
ISN'T ALWAYS FATAL.

489
00:20:32,299 --> 00:20:34,969
AND THERE'S NO WAY TO PREDICT
HOW LONG IT'LL TAKE

490
00:20:35,001 --> 00:20:37,141
ANY ILLNESS
TO CAUSE SOMEONE'S DEATH.

491
00:20:37,169 --> 00:20:39,569
SO, SCIENCE DOESN'T HAVE
ALL THE ANSWERS?

492
00:20:39,606 --> 00:20:41,966
I SUPPOSE NOT.

493
00:20:42,008 --> 00:20:44,638
THAT'S OKAY.

494
00:20:44,677 --> 00:20:46,277
NEITHER DOES GOD.

495
00:20:46,313 --> 00:20:48,683
HE SPENDS MOST OF HIS TIME
TRYING TO FIGURE OUT

496
00:20:48,715 --> 00:20:50,475
WHY WE DO
THE CRAZY THINGS WE DO.

497
00:20:50,517 --> 00:20:53,917
THAT'S WHY HE MADE
BRAIN SCIENTISTS LIKE YOU --

498
00:20:53,953 --> 00:20:55,663
TO HELP HIM
FIGURE IT ALL OUT.

499
00:20:55,688 --> 00:20:57,058
HEY.
SORRY TO INTERRUPT.

500
00:20:57,089 --> 00:20:58,259
I NEED TO GET BACK
TO THE OFFICE.

501
00:20:58,291 --> 00:20:59,591
WHAT'S GOING ON?

502
00:20:59,626 --> 00:21:02,226
CPD found a witness
in K-Town

503
00:21:02,261 --> 00:21:06,171
who said they saw a guy roughing
up Jared Baker a few days ago.

504
00:21:06,198 --> 00:21:07,298
We're looking for him now.

505
00:21:07,334 --> 00:21:08,904
LISTEN, UM...

506
00:21:08,935 --> 00:21:10,595
CALL ME ANYTIME

507
00:21:10,637 --> 00:21:13,807
ABOUT YOUR HEALTH
OR JUST TO TALK.

508
00:21:13,840 --> 00:21:16,310
THANKS.
I'LL DO THAT.

509
00:21:16,343 --> 00:21:18,013
[ BACH'S "PARTITA NO. 6
IN E MINOR" PLAYS ]

510
00:21:18,044 --> 00:21:21,014
Daniel: HOW COULD SUCH
AN INTELLIGENT, LEVEL-HEADED KID

511
00:21:21,047 --> 00:21:22,817
BE SO MEDIEVAL AT HEART?

512
00:21:22,849 --> 00:21:25,019
NOT TO MENTION KATE.

513
00:21:25,051 --> 00:21:28,191
DANIEL, THAT MAN
WHO'S MUSIC YOU'RE PLAYING

514
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:29,820
WAS A DEVOUT BELIEVER.

515
00:21:29,856 --> 00:21:33,326
BACH LIVED 300 YEARS AGO.
SCIENCE WAS IN THE CRADLE.

516
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,830
ISN'T SCIENCE
JUST ANOTHER KIND OF FAITH

517
00:21:35,862 --> 00:21:38,032
WITH ITS OWN SCRIPTURES
AND ITS OWN DOGMAS?

518
00:21:38,064 --> 00:21:40,034
SCIENCE IS BASED ON FACT.

519
00:21:40,066 --> 00:21:42,596
IT MUST BE EXHAUSTING
TO BE SO CYNICAL ALL THE TIME.

520
00:21:42,635 --> 00:21:45,765
IT'S NOT CYNICISM --
IT'S REALITY.

521
00:21:45,805 --> 00:21:49,335
AND, OF COURSE, WE ALL KNOW WHAT
A FIRM GRIP YOU HAVE ON REALITY.

522
00:21:49,376 --> 00:21:51,476
OH, THAT'S VERY FUNNY.

523
00:21:51,511 --> 00:21:53,081
I THINK YOU'RE JEALOUS
OF PEOPLE WITH FAITH.

524
00:21:53,112 --> 00:21:55,552
YOU WISH YOU COULD FIND
THAT KIND OF SOLACE AND COMFORT.

525
00:21:55,582 --> 00:21:56,982
[ MUSIC RESUMES ]

526
00:21:57,016 --> 00:21:58,986
LISTEN TO THAT TREBLE.]

527
00:21:59,018 --> 00:22:01,848
HMM? LIKE A CHICKEN
SCREAMING FOR ITS LIFE.

528
00:22:01,888 --> 00:22:05,558
I'VE SEEN YOU LOOKING LONGINGLY
AT A SATIN-FINISH EBONY GRAND

529
00:22:05,592 --> 00:22:07,562
IN THE STEINWAY SHOWROOM
DOWNTOWN.

530
00:22:07,594 --> 00:22:10,364
YEAH, WELL, THAT PARTICULAR
SATIN-FINISH EBONY GRAND

531
00:22:10,397 --> 00:22:12,057
COSTS AS MUCH
AS MOST CARS.

532
00:22:12,098 --> 00:22:14,868
DANIEL, YOU JUST GOT A CHECK
FOR $50,000.

533
00:22:14,901 --> 00:22:17,371
YOU CAN BUY ANYTHING
YOU WANT WITH IT.

534
00:22:17,404 --> 00:22:19,744
THAT WOULD BE
AN INSANE INDULGENCE.

535
00:22:19,772 --> 00:22:21,812
YOU'VE DONE
CRAZIER THINGS.

536
00:22:21,841 --> 00:22:24,241
YOU REALLY THINK
I SHOULD BUY IT?

537
00:22:24,276 --> 00:22:27,246
HEY, DOC. KYLE JENSEN'S MOTHER
IS ON THE PHONE.

538
00:22:27,279 --> 00:22:28,849
SHE SOUNDS PRETTY UPSET.

539
00:22:31,551 --> 00:22:34,751
Sandy: [ Voice breaking ]
KYLE RUNS UP AND DOWN THOSE
STAIRS 20 TIMES A DAY.

540
00:22:34,787 --> 00:22:37,887
HE MUST HAVE GONE INTO ONE
OF HIS TRANCES AN[ SIGHS ]

541
00:22:37,924 --> 00:22:39,864
WHY WOULD GOD CHOOSE
A MOMENT LIKE THAT?

542
00:22:39,892 --> 00:22:42,032
Dr. Goldsby:
MR. AND MRS. SHELBY,

543
00:22:42,061 --> 00:22:44,501
KYLE SUFFERED A MAJOR
HEAD TRAUMA IN THE FALL,

544
00:22:44,531 --> 00:22:46,901
CAUSING HIS BRAIN
TO BLEED.

545
00:22:46,933 --> 00:22:48,903
IN A WAY, THE FALL
MAY HAVE BEEN FORTUNATE

546
00:22:48,935 --> 00:22:50,595
BECAUSE THE SCAN
REVEALED SOMETHING

547
00:22:50,637 --> 00:22:52,907
WE MIGHT NOT HAVE CAUGHT
UNTIL IT WAS TOO LATE.

548
00:22:52,939 --> 00:22:57,409
KYLE HAS AN INVASIVE TUMOR
IN HIS LEFT TEMPORAL LOBE.

549
00:22:57,444 --> 00:22:59,714
IT'S POSSIBLE THE FALL
DISLODGED IT,

550
00:22:59,746 --> 00:23:01,806
WHICH IS WHAT'S CAUSING
THE SEVERE BLEEDING.

551
00:23:03,049 --> 00:23:04,519
LORD IN HEAVEN.

552
00:23:04,551 --> 00:23:05,721
[ SIGHS ] THAT'S WHAT
YOU TOLD US YESTERDAY.

553
00:23:05,752 --> 00:23:07,792
WE SHOULD HAVE
LISTENED TO YOU.

554
00:23:07,820 --> 00:23:09,520
WE SHOULD HAVE -- WE SHOULD HAVE
BROUGHT HIM IN FOR TESTS.

555
00:23:09,556 --> 00:23:11,286
I NEED TO OPERATE
IMMEDIATELY

556
00:23:11,323 --> 00:23:13,433
TO RELIEVE THE PRESSURE
FROM THE BLEEDING.

557
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:16,030
IF WE CAN REMOVE THE TUMOR,
WE WILL.

558
00:23:16,062 --> 00:23:18,202
KYLE MADE IT CLEAR THAT
HE DIDN'T WANT TO DO ANYTHING

559
00:23:18,230 --> 00:23:20,000
THAT MIGHT CUT HIM OFF
FROM GOD.

560
00:23:20,032 --> 00:23:22,902
YOU CAN'T LEAVE A DISLODGED
TUMOR INSIDE YOUR SON'S BRAIN.

561
00:23:22,935 --> 00:23:24,795
I'M JUST THINKING
OF WHAT KYLE WOULD WANT.

562
00:23:24,837 --> 00:23:26,137
YOU MIGHT AS WELL
SHOOT HIM IN THE HEAD!

563
00:23:26,172 --> 00:23:27,172
DANIEL.

564
00:23:27,206 --> 00:23:28,676
Sandy:
DR. PIERCE IS RIGHT.

565
00:23:28,708 --> 00:23:32,378
[ Crying ] I KNOW KYLE
MAY BE ANGRY WITH ME,

566
00:23:32,411 --> 00:23:36,581
BUT I AM NOT GOING TO
LOSE MY SON.

567
00:23:36,616 --> 00:23:38,046
WE'LL PREP HIM
FOR SURGERY.

568
00:23:39,852 --> 00:23:42,422
DOCTOR, DID --

569
00:23:42,455 --> 00:23:44,655
DID KYLE HAVE ELEVATED PROLACTIN
LEVELS WHEN HE CAME IN?

570
00:23:44,691 --> 00:23:47,331
NO. THEY WERE NORMAL,
BUT NEED TO GET STARTED, SO...

571
00:23:47,359 --> 00:23:49,559
WHAT WAS THAT ABOUT?

572
00:23:49,596 --> 00:23:52,896
ELEVATED PROLACTIN WOULD MEAN
THAT KYLE HAD A SEIZURE

573
00:23:52,932 --> 00:23:54,832
IN THE LAST COUPLE OF HOURS,
BUT HE DIDN'T.

574
00:23:54,867 --> 00:23:57,337
SO HE DIDN'T FALL
BECAUSE HE WENT INTO A TRANCE.

575
00:23:57,369 --> 00:23:59,569
MAYBE HE FIGURED OUT
WHO KILLED JARED.

576
00:23:59,606 --> 00:24:01,106
AND SOMEONE PUSHED HIM.

577
00:24:13,252 --> 00:24:15,622
Kate: DID ANY OF YOU
SEE KYLE FALL?

578
00:24:15,655 --> 00:24:17,285
I WAS IN THE DEN,
READING, AND --

579
00:24:17,323 --> 00:24:20,963
AND, UH, HEARD A CRASH
AND RAN INTO THE FOYER.

580
00:24:20,993 --> 00:24:23,803
JAKE AND TINA CAME TO MY ROOM
AND TOLD ME WHAT HAPPENED.

581
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:27,800
I WAS MAKING DINNER,
AND I HEARD TOM YELL FOR HELP.

582
00:24:27,834 --> 00:24:30,644
WHEN I SAW HIM ON THE GROUND,
ALL THAT BLOOD, I --

583
00:24:30,670 --> 00:24:32,140
[ CELEXCUSE ME.GS ]

584
00:24:32,171 --> 00:24:33,471
MORETTI.

585
00:24:33,506 --> 00:24:35,466
WHY'S SHE ASKING
ALL THESE QUESTIONS?

586
00:24:35,508 --> 00:24:37,978
NOBODY IN THE HOUSE
WOULD WANT TO HURT KYLE.

587
00:24:38,010 --> 00:24:39,310
ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

588
00:24:39,345 --> 00:24:41,045
Kate: DANIEL.

589
00:24:44,250 --> 00:24:45,890
THEY FOUND THE GUY WHO
BEAT UP JARED IN K-TOWN.

590
00:24:45,918 --> 00:24:48,018
WHAT ABOUT KYLE?

591
00:24:48,054 --> 00:24:49,524
WELL, THE FAMILY WILL CALL US
IF THERE'S ANY NEWS.

592
00:24:49,556 --> 00:24:51,716
NO, I MEAN
ABOUT PROTECTING HIM.

593
00:24:51,758 --> 00:24:53,528
SOMEBODY TRIED TO KILL HIM.
THEY MAY TRY AGAIN.

594
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:55,160
YOU -- YOU GOT TO PUT
A GUARD ON HIM.

595
00:24:55,194 --> 00:24:56,904
DANIEL, I'M NOT GONNA BE ABLE
TO GET APPROVAL FOR A GUARD

596
00:24:56,929 --> 00:24:58,529
ON A HOSPITAL ROOM 24/7

597
00:24:58,565 --> 00:25:01,395
JUST BECAUSE WE HAVE
AN UNSUBSTANTIATED THEORY.

598
00:25:01,433 --> 00:25:03,343
[ SIGHS ]
WELL, I'M STAYING.

599
00:25:04,537 --> 00:25:06,367
ALL RIGHT.

600
00:25:07,774 --> 00:25:09,744
Aaron: ARE YOU SAYING
THAT I KILLED JARED BAKER?

601
00:25:09,776 --> 00:25:12,306
WITNESSES SAW YOU TWO
GET INTO A SHOVING MATCH

602
00:25:12,344 --> 00:25:14,314
A FEW DAYS
BEFORE HE WAS MURDERED.

603
00:25:14,346 --> 00:25:17,016
LOOK, I DO OUTREACH
FOR THE V.A.,

604
00:25:17,049 --> 00:25:18,119
AND WE GET A LOT
OF THESE VETS

605
00:25:18,150 --> 00:25:19,690
LIVING ON THE STREET
AROUND HERE,

606
00:25:19,719 --> 00:25:22,149
SO, YEAH, IT [BLEEP] ME OFF
WHEN THESE [BLEEP] COME DOWN

607
00:25:22,188 --> 00:25:24,658
AND TRY TO SCAM THESE GUYS
OUT OF THEIR SDI CHECKS.

608
00:25:24,691 --> 00:25:27,331
JARED BAKER
WAS SCAMMING VETERANS?

609
00:25:27,359 --> 00:25:29,329
PASSING OUT PAMPHLETS,
HAWKING SOME CHURCH

610
00:25:29,361 --> 00:25:31,661
THAT'S ABOUT DONATING
EVERY CENT THEY GOT,

611
00:25:31,698 --> 00:25:32,928
SO I TOSSED HIS PAMPHLETS

612
00:25:32,965 --> 00:25:34,695
AND TOLD HIM
TO TAKE HIS SCAM ELSEWHERE.

613
00:25:34,734 --> 00:25:37,174
AND THEN WHEN HE DIDN'T GET
THE MESSAGE, YOU GOT PHYSICAL.

614
00:25:38,871 --> 00:25:41,171
AFTER HE TOOK OFF, I FELT BAD
ABOUT THE WHOLE THING,

615
00:25:41,207 --> 00:25:43,137
SO I FISHED ONE OF THE PAMPHLETS
OUT OF THE TRASH

616
00:25:43,175 --> 00:25:44,275
AND TOOK A LOOK.

617
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:46,280
AND GUESS WHAT --
I WAS RIGHT.

618
00:25:46,312 --> 00:25:47,652
IT'S ALL A BIG FAKE --

619
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:49,120
AT LEAST THE SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN IS.

620
00:25:50,116 --> 00:25:51,776
THAT PLACE
DOES NOT EXIST.

621
00:25:51,818 --> 00:25:54,448
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

622
00:25:54,486 --> 00:25:55,686
PICTURE IN THE PAMPHLET.

623
00:25:55,722 --> 00:25:58,022
SCHOOLKIDS
IN FRONT OF A BIG LAKE?

624
00:25:58,057 --> 00:25:59,557
SCHOOL'S SUPPOSED TO BE
IN MAIMANA.

625
00:25:59,592 --> 00:26:02,802
I WAS STATIONED IN HERAT,
A STONE'S THROW FROM THERE.

626
00:26:02,829 --> 00:26:05,199
THERE'S NO LAKE IN THAT VALLEY,
JUST SAND.

627
00:26:05,231 --> 00:26:07,031
THIS PICTURE?

628
00:26:07,066 --> 00:26:08,526
YEAH.

629
00:26:10,269 --> 00:26:11,899
SEE THE WRITING
ON THE BLACKBOARD?

630
00:26:11,938 --> 00:26:13,108
THAT'S FARSI.

631
00:26:13,139 --> 00:26:14,869
IN MAIMANA,
THEY SPEAK ARABIC.

632
00:26:14,907 --> 00:26:16,907
I CALLED A BUNCH OF GUYS
WHO SERVED OVER THERE.

633
00:26:16,943 --> 00:26:18,813
NOBODY EVER HEARD
OF AN INTERNATIONAL GROUP

634
00:26:18,845 --> 00:26:20,575
OPERATING A SCHOOL
ANYWHERE NEAR MAIMANA.

635
00:26:20,613 --> 00:26:22,823
YOU REPORT THIS TO ANYONE?

636
00:26:22,849 --> 00:26:24,549
JUST JARED BAKER.

637
00:26:24,583 --> 00:26:26,823
WAIT. JARED KNEW?

638
00:26:26,853 --> 00:26:28,493
NEXT TIME HE CAME DOWN
TO K-TOWN,

639
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:30,490
I TOLD HIM
EXACTLY WHAT I JUST TOLD YOU.

640
00:26:30,522 --> 00:26:31,822
HOW DID HE TAKE IT?

641
00:26:31,858 --> 00:26:33,488
IT SHOOK HIM UP.

642
00:26:33,525 --> 00:26:35,225
HE SAID HE WANTED TO REPORT IT
TO SOMEBODY,

643
00:26:35,261 --> 00:26:37,001
SO I TOLD HIM
HE SHOULD START WITH THE I.R.S.

644
00:26:37,029 --> 00:26:40,269
THE I.R.S. GAVE HAVEN HOUSE
A CLEAN BILL OF HEALTH.

645
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:56,750
LAST-MINUTE VACATION,
ETHAN?

646
00:26:58,651 --> 00:27:01,791
WE REMOVED THE TUMOR
AND STOPPED THE BLEEDING.

647
00:27:01,821 --> 00:27:02,961
[ SIGHS ]

648
00:27:02,989 --> 00:27:06,259
BUT THERE WERE
COMPLICATIONS.

649
00:27:06,292 --> 00:27:07,932
KYLE SUFFERED
A RUPTURED ANEURYSM.

650
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:09,260
HE'S IN A COMA.

651
00:27:09,295 --> 00:27:11,925
[ SOBS ]
OH, MY GOD.

652
00:27:11,964 --> 00:27:14,904
THE SITUATION
WIDOESN'T LOOK GOOD.?

653
00:27:17,704 --> 00:27:19,074
COULD HE DIE?

654
00:27:19,105 --> 00:27:22,105
I THINK YOU NEED TO
PREPARE YOURSELVES

655
00:27:22,141 --> 00:27:24,541
FOR THAT POSSIBILITY.

656
00:27:24,576 --> 00:27:25,636
I'M SORRY.

657
00:27:25,678 --> 00:27:27,148
[ CRYING ]

658
00:27:27,179 --> 00:27:30,319
SURE.
I'LL TAKE YOU IN.

659
