WE PULLED IT OFF.

884
00:37:53,204 --> 00:37:54,774
UNTIL JARED BAKER
STARTED ASKING QUESTIONS

885
00:37:54,806 --> 00:37:56,166
ABOUT THE SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN.

886
00:37:56,207 --> 00:37:58,507
YEAH,
AFTER I TALKED TO JARED,

887
00:37:58,544 --> 00:38:03,324
I CALLED UP NIKKI, AND I TOLD
HER WE HAD A PROBLEM.

888
00:38:03,349 --> 00:38:06,689
NEXT DAY,
JARED TURNS UP DEAD.

889
00:38:06,718 --> 00:38:09,318
I CALLED HER, AND I SAID,
"WHAT THE [BLEEP] IS GOING ON?

890
00:38:09,355 --> 00:38:11,015
NO ONE'S
SUPPOSED TO GET HURT."

891
00:38:11,056 --> 00:38:14,956
SHE TOLD ME TO KEEP QUIET
AND TO GET OUT OF TOWN.

892
00:38:14,993 --> 00:38:16,963
SO I WENT HOME,
AND I GOT MY BAGS.

893
00:38:16,995 --> 00:38:18,325
YOU GUYS PICKED ME UP.

894
00:38:18,364 --> 00:38:21,834
AND THAT IS THE ENTIRE STORY.
I SWEAR.

895
00:38:21,867 --> 00:38:25,837
JUST ONE PROBLEM --
IT'S YOUR WORD AGAINST HERS.

896
00:38:25,871 --> 00:38:29,581
I MIGHT BE AN IDIOT,
BUT I AM NOT STUPID.

897
00:38:31,242 --> 00:38:33,552
CHECK THE LINING
IN MY SUITCASE.

898
00:38:33,579 --> 00:38:36,549
THERE'S A FLASH DRIVE
WITH SOME SOUND FILES ON IT.

899
00:38:36,582 --> 00:38:39,052
ONE THING YOU LEARN
WHEN YOU WORK FOR THE I.R.S.,

900
00:38:39,084 --> 00:38:41,854
YOUR WHOLE LIFE IS THE VALUE
OF KEEPING GOOD RECORDS.

901
00:38:45,591 --> 00:38:47,731
NIKKI: They aren't buying
that Shane killed Jared.

902
00:38:47,759 --> 00:38:49,859
Oh, baby, calm down.

903
00:38:49,895 --> 00:38:51,555
Okay.
We're going to be all right.

904
00:38:51,597 --> 00:38:53,127
I've got the room all booked

905
00:38:53,164 --> 00:38:55,004
on the most beautiful beach
in the Maldives.

906
00:38:55,033 --> 00:38:57,973
KYLE:
Nikki, what's going on?
Who are you talking to?

907
00:38:58,003 --> 00:38:59,473
NIKKI:
Hey. I-I got to go.

908
00:38:59,505 --> 00:39:01,465
No, I think Kyle heard me.
Okay.

909
00:39:01,507 --> 00:39:03,777
I love you.
I'll see you at the airport.

910
00:39:03,809 --> 00:39:05,939
KYLE WANTED TO KNOW
WHY YOU WERE TALKING TO US.

911
00:39:05,977 --> 00:39:07,977
THAT'S WHY
HE KNOCKED ON YOUR DOOR.

912
00:39:08,013 --> 00:39:09,583
Kate:
BUT HE OVERHEARD TOO MUCH,

913
00:39:09,615 --> 00:39:11,815
AND THAT'S WHY YOU PUSHED HIM
DOWN THE STAIRS.

914
00:39:11,850 --> 00:39:13,320
DO YOU THINK I DON'T KNOW

915
00:39:13,351 --> 00:39:15,851
THAT A SOUND RECORDING
CAN BE MANIPULATED?

916
00:39:17,423 --> 00:39:19,993
DO YOU EVEN KNOW THAT
YOU'RE DOING SATAN'S WORK?

917
00:39:22,293 --> 00:39:25,763
PLEASE, GOD, I PRAY THAT YOU
WILL FORGIVE THESE PEOPLE

918
00:39:25,797 --> 00:39:27,097
FOR THEIR BLINDNESS.

919
00:39:27,132 --> 00:39:29,272
I PRAY THAT YOU WILL
SHOW THEM THE TRUTH.

920
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:31,400
WHILE YOU'RE AT IT,
YOU MIGHT WANT TO ALSO PRAY

921
00:39:31,437 --> 00:39:34,407
FOR A JUDGE WHO DOESN'T
BELIEVE IN THE DEATH PENALTY.

922
00:39:36,041 --> 00:39:38,511
Dr. Goldsby:
IT'S A MIRACLE, REALLY.

923
00:39:38,544 --> 00:39:40,514
KYLE'S AWAKE
AND EATING CHOCOLATE PUDDING

924
00:39:40,546 --> 00:39:41,676
LIKE THERE'S NO TOMORROW.

925
00:39:41,713 --> 00:39:43,013
HOW MUCH TISSUE DAMAGE?

926
00:39:43,048 --> 00:39:44,218
SOME SWELLING.

927
00:39:44,249 --> 00:39:45,849
HE'LL NEED TO TAKE IT EASY
FOR A WHILE,

928
00:39:45,884 --> 00:39:47,424
BUT HE SHOULD MAKE
A GOOD RECOVERY.

929
00:39:47,453 --> 00:39:48,523
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

930
00:39:55,894 --> 00:39:59,874
THAT MESSAGE YOU SENT GOD
MUST HAVE DONE THE TRICK.

931
00:39:59,898 --> 00:40:03,028
SOMETIMES HE NEEDS
A KICK IN THE PANTS.

932
00:40:03,068 --> 00:40:05,868
PEOPLE MAKE AMAZING RECOVERIES
ALL THE TIME

933
00:40:05,904 --> 00:40:08,644
WITH NO HELP
FROM SOME NONEXISTENT DEITY.

934
00:40:08,674 --> 00:40:12,214
IF HE DOESN'T EXIST, THEN WHY
WOULD YOU SEND HIM A MESSAGE?

935
00:40:13,712 --> 00:40:15,712
BECAUSE I'M A STARK,
RAVING LUNATIC.

936
00:40:18,484 --> 00:40:21,454
LOOK, ARE CLOSING
HAVEN HOUSE,

937
00:40:21,487 --> 00:40:23,417
BUT WE'RE KEEPING
THE BROKEN PROMISE,

938
00:40:23,455 --> 00:40:25,185
OPENING A SCHOOL
IN AFGHANISTAN.

939
00:40:26,424 --> 00:40:28,094
I KNOW IT'S WHAT GOD WANTS.

940
00:40:28,126 --> 00:40:30,826
YOU'RE STILL HEARING A VOICE
EVEN AFTER THE OPERATION?

941
00:40:30,862 --> 00:40:34,332
NOT AN ACTUAL VOICE IN MY HEAD
LIKE BEFORE.

942
00:40:34,365 --> 00:40:37,665
BUT I STILL HEAR GOD
EVERY SECOND...

943
00:40:37,703 --> 00:40:39,773
THE WAY ANYBODY CAN
IF THEY JUST LISTEN.

944
00:40:46,512 --> 00:40:49,522
HERE.

945
00:40:52,718 --> 00:40:55,248
MAYBE THIS WILL BUY A FEW BOOKS
FOR THE NEW SCHOOL.

946
00:40:58,456 --> 00:40:59,856
WOW!

947
00:40:59,891 --> 00:41:01,731
THAT'S A LOT OF BOOKS.

948
00:41:03,394 --> 00:41:05,704
DOES THIS MEAN
YOU BELIEVE IN GOD NOW?

949
00:41:05,731 --> 00:41:07,831
ABSOLUTELY NOT.

950
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,900
BUT I BELIEVE IN YOU.

951
00:41:12,671 --> 00:41:16,841
I GOT SOMETHING
FOR YOU, TOO.

952
00:41:18,744 --> 00:41:21,714
KYLE, WHAT KIND
OF PRESENT IS THAT?

953
00:41:21,747 --> 00:41:23,877
I THINK DR. PIERCE
WILL APPRECIATE IT.

954
00:41:23,915 --> 00:41:25,915
[ CHUCKLES ]

